</p><textarea readonly="" accesskey="," id="wpTextbox1" cols="80" rows="25" style="" class="mw-editfont-monospace" lang="en" dir="ltr" name="wpTextbox1">  '''"Linked Data, Language Technologies and Multilingual Content Analytics" 2nd LIDER roadmapping workshop'''
   
