** Christian Chiarcos (University Frankfurt am Main, Germany): [[Media:Lider-workshop-20140509-olwg-chiarcos.pdf| Open Linguistics Working Group of the OKF]]

* '''9:45 - 10:45''' Panel 3 on "'''Data and Metadata of Language Resources as Linked Data on the Web'''”. Chair: Jorge Gracia (UPM, Spain). Speakers:
